mod_list.mod:
https://forge.sp-tarkov.com/mod/2399/inventory-organizing-features-ported-to-40x

Adds several inventory organizing features which rely on item tags, such as sort locking, move locking and container organizing. Also adds a button to take out all the items from a container.

@o
Organize. Makes a container pull items which can fit into it. Items which are being pulled are determined by container’s filters and parameters which user has specified.

@o ;
Collects the specific category only. Like "@o money;" (without quotes). NOTICE the SEMICOLON is important, and the bracket isn’t needed.

@o !;
Collects everything except the specific category. Like "@o !ammo;" (without quotes), which collects everything except ammo.

@o n:
;
Collects items which name contains the given string. Like "@o n:5.45;" (without quotes), which collects all items with "5.45" in their name.

@o |;
Collects items matching either condition 1 or condition 2. Like "@o n:7.62|n:5.45;" (without quotes), which collects all items with "7.62" or "5.45" in their name.
